claude "Add a fixed 64px nav bar to both my client portal and user portal files. Top-left: Linkwright logo linking to index.html. Top-right: Back to main site link. Style: background #F4F1EC 95% opacity, backdrop blur, 0.5px bottom border rgba(26,24,20,0.1), DM Sans font, charcoal #1A1814. Add padding-top 64px to body. Mobile friendly. Use the same L-bracket SVG logo from the main landing page."
lsadd a fixed nav bar to client-portal.html and user-portal.html with the Linkwright logo top-left linking to index.html and a back to main site link top-right. Style: cream background #F4F1EC, DM Sans font, charcoal #1A1814, 64px height, backdrop blur. Add padding-top 64px to body on both files.

